Rapha\u235\'ebl Bastide\line }{{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "http://github.com/raphaelbastide" }\cs17\i\ai{\fldrslt \cf2\ul\ulc0\langfe255\alang255\lang255\rtlch \ltrch\loch
