\par \pard\plain \s19\sb0\sa120{\cs17\i\ai\rtlch \ltrch\loch
Apertus Axiom will be the first ever open digital cinema camera designed from scratch with openness in mind. The image sensor of choice is the CMV12000 from Cmosis. To ultimately }{\cs17\i\ai\rtlch \ltrch\loch
